POST-INSTALL:

		* Add the following environment variable:
		export ERL_RUN_TOP=/usr/lib/erlang

		* Each time you need to use 'otp_base', invoke
		a new instance of it like this:
		$ otp_base

		This will create a clean copy of the framework on 
		/tmp/otp_base$$ (where $$ is procid)

INFO:
		* Read the excellent article describing 'otp_base' usage 
		written by Martin Logan at:
		http://wiki.trapexit.org/index.php/Building_An_OTP_Application
